{"lemma":"رِسالَةٌ","slug":"رِسالَةٌ","root":"ر.س.ل","root_slug":"ر-س-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-س-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"رِسالَة","root":"رسل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":10},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n15500","n15501"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%90%D8%B3%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"message","examples":[{"text":"أُبَلِّغُكُمْ رِسَالَاتِ رَبِّي وَأَنْصَحُ لَكُمْ وَأَعْلَمُ مِنَ ٱللّٰهِ مَا لَا تَعْلَمُونَ","english":"I communicate the messages of my Lord to you and I am your well-wisher, and I know from God what you do not know."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"letter (message)"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ri.saː.la/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n15500","headword_ar":"رَسَالَةٌ","root":"rsl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n15501","headword_ar":"رِسَالَةٌ","root":"rsl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rasaAlapN","text_ar":"رَسَالَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rasuwlN","text_ar":"رَسُولٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rasiylN","text_ar":"رَسِيلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Th, M, K) signify the same, (S, M, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A message;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a letter;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA in explanation of the first, and KL in explanation of the first and third;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a communication sent from one person or party to another, oral or written;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] substs. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arosala","text_ar":"اَرْسَلَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilayohi","text_ar":"اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K: *) the pl. of the first is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rasaAy^ilu","text_ar":"رَسَايِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arosulN","text_ar":"اَرْسُلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rasuwlN","text_ar":"رَسُولٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"risaAlapN","text_ar":"رِسَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and of the fem. gender. (TA. [See the former of the two verses cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rasuwlN","text_ar":"رَسُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arosalotu fulaAnFA fiY risaAlapK","text_ar":"اَرْسَلْتُ فُلَانًا فِى رِسَالَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arosala A_ilayohi","text_ar":"اَرْسَلَ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rasuwlFA","text_ar":"رَسُولًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (MA:) see 4. A poet says, (S,) namely El-Ash'ar El-Joafee, (TA,)"},{"kind":"quote","text":"↓ \n      A^alaA A^abolgo A^abaA EamorKw rasuwlFA\n                      \n                     \n                        biA^an~iY Eano futaAHatikumo ganiY~u"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Now deliver thou to Aboo-' Amr a message, saying that I am in no need of your judging"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baniY EamorKw","text_ar":"بَنِى عَمْرٍو"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the sons of ' Amr"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: he means,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano Hukomkumo","text_ar":"عَنْ حُكْمكُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And hence the saying of Kutheiyir,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"laqado ka*aba AlwaA$uwna maA buHotu Einodahumo\n                      \n                     ↓ \n      bisir~K walaA A^arosalotuhumo birasuwli"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Assuredly the slanderers have lied: I revealed not in their presence a secret, nor did I send them with a message"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, TA:) or, as some relate the second hemistich, (TA,)"},{"kind":"quote","text":"↓ \n      bilayolaY walaA A^arosalotuhumo birasiyli"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. I revealed not the case of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Leyla, nor did I send them with a message"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: thus cited by Th. (M, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"risaAlapN","text_ar":"رِسَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A tract,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small treatise"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discourse;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majal~ap","text_ar":"مَجَلَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"book,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"writing, relating to science,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on any subject."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"comprising a few questions, inquiries,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"problems, of one kind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rasaAy^ilu","text_ar":"رَسَايِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Apostleship;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"apostolic office"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"function."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^um~u risaAlapa","text_ar":"اُمُّ رِسَالَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in a copy of the K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^um~u risaAlapK","text_ar":"اُمُّ رِسَالَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxamap","text_ar":"رَخَمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"female of the vultur percnopterus,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHomap","text_ar":"رَحْمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (M, K, TA:) a surname thereof. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","Msb","K","Th","MA","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}